javadoc: Action to undo checkouts for domain files in the repository.

methods.name: <init>
methods.comment: Creates an action to undo checkouts for domain files in the repository.

params.name: plugin
params.comment: the plug-in that owns this action.

params.name: provider
params.comment: provides a list of domain files to be affected by this action.

methods.javadoc: Returns true if at least one of the provided domain files is checked out from the repository.
methods.name: isEnabledForContext
methods.comment: Returns true if at least one of the provided domain files is checked out from the repository.

methods.javadoc:
Gets the domain files from the provider and then undoes the checkout on any that are 
 checked out.
methods.name: undoCheckOut
methods.comment:
Gets the domain files from the provider and then undoes the checkout on any that are 
 checked out.

methods.name: undoCheckOuts
methods.comment:
Displays the undo checkout confirmation dialog for each checked out file and then 
 undoes the checkout while keeping a copy of the working version of the file if the 
 user chooses to do so.
 All unmodified checkouts will be undone. Only modified checkouts the user chooses
 will be undone.

params.name: modifiedArchivesList
params.comment: the list of checked out files that have been modified

name: VersionControlDataTypeArchiveUndoCheckoutAction
comment: Action to undo checkouts for domain files in the repository.
